Dr. Ronald M SegaProfessorResearch InterestsSystems EngineeringContact InformationOffice: Engineering AR204Phone: 970-491-7067Fax: 970-491-2249Email: ron.sega@colostate.eduEducationB.S. 1974 Air Force Academy in Mathematics and PhysicsM.S. 1975 The Ohio State University in PhysicsPh.D 1982 University of Colorado in Electrical EngineeringFellow: American Institute of Aeronautics and Astronautics (AIAA), IEEE Institute of Electrical and Electronic Engineers (IEEE) Publications and Citations of Published Work










