Ronald M. Sega - Wikipedia






















 






Ronald M. Sega

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Ronald Michael Sega





NASA Astronaut


Nationality
American


Status
Retired


Born
(1952-12-04) December 4, 1952 (age 64)
Macedonia, Ohio



Other occupation

Engineer


Rank
Major General, USAF



Time in space

17d 12h 25m


